Academic references
===================

RaiSim's deformable-object solver uses XPBD/PBD concepts described in:

Miles Macklin, Matthias Muller, and Nuttapong Chentanez. "XPBD: Position-Based
Simulation of Compliant Constrained Dynamics." Proceedings of the 9th
International Conference on Motion in Games (MIG 2016), pages 49-54.
DOI: 10.1145/2994258.2994272

